---
title: "_setAssetOut (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_live: _whenNoLiveAuctions()
    q_check_live --> q_revert_live: live auction exists
    q_revert_live --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_live --> q_check_zero: no live auctions
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: assetOut == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress
    q_check_zero --> q_check_same: assetOut != address(0)
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: currentAssetOut == assetOut
    q_revert_same --> [*]: revert ValueNotUpdated
    q_check_same --> q_update: currentAssetOut != assetOut
    q_update --> q_cleanup: s_assetOut = assetOut
    q_cleanup --> q_emit: delete s_assetParams[currentAssetOut]
    q_emit --> [*]: emit AssetOutSet

    note right of q_update
        INV-001: Old assetOut params are deleted on change
        INV-002: No configuration changes during live auctions
    end note
